Kiana Sādāt-Hosseini renowned as Little Kiana or Kiana of Nishapur also The Seven-year-old Kiana (2009–2016) was an Iranian seven-year Preschool student from Nishapur. She was kidnapped, raped and murdered by her aunt's husband Mehdi N in September 15, 2016. He was hanged in public 15 days later in September 30, 2016 in Nishapur with a special court order signed by Sadegh Larijani.
